# Tests for src/main/java changes

When you add or change a class under `backend/src/main/java/com/aidecision/agentic/`:

1. Add or update `backend/src/test/java/.../<ClassName>Test.java` in the **same package**.
2. Prefer pure unit tests (no Spring context); mock repos, HTTP, and LLM clients.
3. Name tests `methodName_scenario` (e.g. `evaluate_numericComparison_returnsTrue`).
4. Run `cd backend && mvn -q test -Dtest=<ClassName>Test`.
5. Aim for **100% line coverage** on the changed class (verify with JaCoCo report after `mvn test`).

Do not add tests that only assert constants or trivial getters with no behavior.
